$ Makefile.am

The (manually created) `Makefile.am` is turned into a portable → development/GNU/toolchain/Build-System/Makefile_in[`Makefile.in`] by → development/GNU/toolchain/Build-System/Automake.

{ Example

The `Makefile.am` for the famous *hello world* application might look as follows:
code {
bin_PROGRAMS = hello
hello_SOURCES = hello.c
code }
 

}
